<center><font size=7><b>Exolon</b></font></center>
<center>Number of entries found: 5</center><p>
<center>
<table width=600>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Cheat modes</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD>To use the cheat, first press key 2 for redefine keys. Next type Z O R B A for
the different keys, now repeat this, but with the keys that you want to play the
game with. This gives you infinite lives to blast anything in your path.
 <i>(YS Smash Tips)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Multiface pokes</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD><table border="0">
<tr>
<td WIDTH="200" ALIGN="LEFT"><B><U>DESCRIPTION</B></U></TD>
<td WIDTH="200" ALIGN="LEFT"><B><U>POKE(s)</B></U></TD>
</TR>
<tr><td>Infinite Lives</td><td>40221,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Infinite Ammo</td><td>33646,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Infinite Grenades</td><td>37456,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Double Fire</td><td>33663,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>One Shot</td><td>44074,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Infinite Rockets</td><td>37397,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>No Cannon Fire</td><td>36831,24</td></tr>
<tr><td>No Flying Aliens</td><td>42330,201</td></tr>
<tr><td>Lot of Aliens</td><td>42330,0:42336,24</td></tr>
<tr><td>No Aliens</td><td>42338,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Fast Explode</td><td>35456,0:36845,0:38221,0:42338,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Mines are harmless</td><td>40110,201</td></tr>
</table>
<BR><BR>
The Fast Explode POKE make the grenades detonate immediately. It doesn't look as nice,
but it's handy if you're on a full screen as it doesn't SLOOOWWW the game down so much..
<BR>Just to state the blindingly obvious, you can't select "Lots Of Aliens" and "No Aliens" at the
same time :)
<BR>
Redefine keys as ZOBRA for Infinite Lives<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <i>(Gerard Sweeney in Hack Attack III)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Type-in hacks</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD>This can be found in <a href="ftp://ftp.void.jump.org/pub/sinclair/magazines/SinclairUser/Issue74/Tape/">this issue of Poke City</a>.
 <i>(Cover Tape in Sinclair User issue 74)</i> 

<br><hr>
This can be found in <a href="ftp://ftp.void.jump.org/pub/sinclair/magazines/YourSinclair/Issue40/Tape/">this issue of Pokes</a> in the alphabetical section.
 <i>(Cover Tape in Your Sinclair issue 40)</i> 

<br><hr>
<pre>
 10 CLEAR 25999: LOAD "" CODE
 20 FOR F=23326 TO 1e9
 30 READ A
 40 IF A=999 THEN GO TO 60
 50 POKE F,A: NEXT F
 60 POKE 64531,125
 70 RANDOMIZE USR 64512
 80 POKE 65117,30
 90 RANDOMIZE USR 65082
100 DATA 175
110 DATA 50,158,123: REM AMMO
120 DATA 50,128,128: REM GRENADES
130 DATA 50,77,149: REM LIVES
140 DATA 195,0,91,999: REM END MARKER
</pre>
 <i>(YS Smash Tips)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
</table></center><P>
